description: Deletes the version of the theme that the specified theme alias points to. If you provide a specific alias, you delete the version of the theme that the alias points to.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the theme alias to delete.

parameters.name: ThemeId
parameters.description: The ID for the theme that the specified alias is for.

parameters.name: AliasName
parameters.description: The unique name for the theme alias to delete.

nested_items.name: AliasName
nested_items.description: The name for the theme alias.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the theme resource using the deleted alias.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: ThemeId
nested_items.description: An ID for the theme associated with the deletion.
